{"tid":1803753,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"新版Switch電力加強版，與Switch lite已遭破解","createTime":"2019-12-30T12:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T09:39:40.000Z","uid":58335,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"7b08668bd29e85bfa2ccd0c8029d7220d756e666","tid":1803753,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:27:28.000Z","msg":"在Switch破解問世之後，任天堂就針對已發現的漏洞做修補，基本上算斷了Switch改機的市場，目前以新機來說，在2018年6月之後所修補過的主機都是不能改機的，連最近任天堂推出的電力加強版，與Switch life也不能破解，這情況已持續一陣子，電商平台上可改Switch主機經炒作，售價更是水漲船高，竟飆高至台幣1萬塊以上！<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.zi.org.tw/kocpc/2019/10/1572446258-b122812344b5fdfb4a73153496bf8f1a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.zi.org.tw%2Fkocpc%2F2019%2F10%2F1572446258-b122812344b5fdfb4a73153496bf8f1a.png&h=e3ab65d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，知名遊戲機破解團隊team-xecuter，今天宣佈已成功破解新版任天堂Switch「HAC-001(-01)」，破解了代號為「Mariko」所使用Tegra X1升級晶片的電力加強新版任天堂Switch，與Switch Lite，並且連先前不能破解的舊款機型「HAC-001」問題也一併解決，據傳在近期內將會釋出更多Switch破解消息。<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.zi.org.tw/kocpc/2019/10/1572445470-89e4823475afff0e0f7153686c0de7f5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.zi.org.tw%2Fkocpc%2F2019%2F10%2F1572445470-89e4823475afff0e0f7153686c0de7f5.png&h=986bdd46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這將會為遊戲業界帶來不小的影響，任天堂公司又會怎麼應對？請持續關注本網站的相關報導，<br />\n<br />\n會為您帶來最新的Switch破解相關情報。<br />\n<br />\nP.S 香港改機犯法的<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kocpc.com.tw/archives/289312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kocpc.com.tw%2Farchives%2F289312&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=b04879fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kocpc.com.tw/archives/289312</a>"},{"pid":"bd82d55833579bb804d63966b9e14cf72221cd4a","tid":1803753,"uid":317979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:27:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">德國聯署有三份 呢家仲有一份未達標 最後兩日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1802070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1802070</a><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=57a98a89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"48f6bce279a91f72f1166d6ec0b1cf846018c3ee","tid":1803753,"uid":7332,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:28:34.000Z","msg":"乞衣到 已經少games 仲要破解"},{"pid":"66b0d5ee0af9ee1a3c83c8f83c69681a39d6af21","tid":1803753,"uid":269707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ee731bdbe0e9fedfcac7a63461373614b5283e","tid":1803753,"uid":1654,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:32:18.000Z","msg":"香港物價已經升到買game 唔覺貴"},{"pid":"ea0ef412629b9b05c8d02c45c95b67e81d647bc0","tid":1803753,"uid":48631,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:34:10.000Z","msg":"新版仲係用tegra?咁抵佢死"},{"pid":"813a0120154a5c7f859b58151f86ee8ddddb9057","tid":1803753,"uid":273716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80ee731bdbe0e9fedfcac7a63461373614b5283e","tid":1803753,"uid":1654,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:32:18.000Z","msg":"香港物價已經升到買game 唔覺貴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf8d84de125db3511ea